      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical release used under documented QA plan; FDA in-house solver validated per NIST traceability requirements.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA solvers (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under formal software quality assurance programs with version control, regression testing, and documented release processes. Achieved level exceeds required level for this model risk tier."
